property.description: Welcome to 410 Woodhaven Place, where luxury meets innovation and retreat-style living. This remodeled and stylishly modern JTS home is nestled on a quiet street in West Sacramento's most desired gate community, The Rivers. This home has been designed to perfection with a brand-new resort style pool and spa, high-end finishes inside and out, custom lighting and sound, custom cabinetry, converted 2nd garage into a home gym. Primary suite with two walk-in closets and elegant spa style bathroom is located on the ground floor. Smart home technology is seamlessly integrated for ultimate convenience. Enjoy the park-like community right across the river from downtown Sacramento, with three community pools, walking and biking trails, private playground and picnic areas. 410 Woodhaven Place is not just a home; it's a showcase of upgrades and technological sophistication. Welcome to your forever home.
